title: Dumpling World
description: Serves meat, veg options available. A small Asian restaurant offering some vegetarian and vegan options. Most dishes revolve around their specialty, jiaozi (Chinese dumplings). The vegetarian dumpling is filled with mushroom, tofu, carrot, cabbage encased in a rice noodle shell. Uses no MSG. Eat in or take away. Previously located on Collins St, Feb 2015.
